original_title: Jimmie JJ Walker & Michael Winslow: We Are Still Here
overview: Jimmie Walker (best known for his role as J.J. Evans on the popular sitcom, Good Times), and Michael Winslow (best known for his role in all seven Police Academy films), perform in this hilarious one-hour stand up special featuring incredible stories, jokes, and all the bleeps and bloops you can handle!
title: Jimmie JJ Walker & Michael Winslow: We Are Still Here
